'''弗朗切斯科·鲁利'''（意大利语：Francesco Rulli）是一名[[意大利|意大利]][[实业家|实业家]]，[[慈善家|慈善家]]和{{tsl|en|New York Athletic Club|纽约体育俱乐部}}的黑带[[柔道|柔道]]教练。1995年，他创建了MTI USA公司并担任总裁。2006年，他创办了'''Film Annex'''网站并且同时担任总裁。'''Film Annex'''是一个在线[[独立电影|独立电影]]发行平台和[[网络电视|网络电视]]网络<ref>{{cite web|title=Film Annex|url=http://www.crunchbase.com/company/film-annex|publisher=Crunch Base|accessdate=13 February 2013|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408003000/http://www.crunchbase.com/company/film-annex|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2014年，他推出了[[比特币|比特币]]平台[http://www.bitLanders.com bitLanders] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bitlanders.com/ |date=20200814204928 }}，并担任总裁<ref>{{cite web|title=Interview with Bitlanders CEO Francesco Rulli|url=http://bitcoinist.net/interview-bitlanders-ceo-francesco-rulli|publisher=Bitcoinist|accessdate=4 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415033820/http://bitcoinist.net/interview-bitlanders-ceo-francesco-rulli/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。弗朗切斯科·鲁利还共同创立了由[[美国|美国]][[演员|演员]]，[[制片人|制片人]]和[[导演|导演]][[约翰·马克维奇|约翰·马克维奇]]所创设的[[时尚|时尚]]和[[设计|设计]]咨询公司“马德夫人”（Mrs. Mudd）<ref>{{cite web|first=Heather|last=John|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2003/apr/13/magazine/tm-malkovich15|title=Fashionable Liaisons: Meet John Malkovich, Tailor of the Cinema|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=April 13, 2003|accessdate=January 24, 2012|archive-date=2013-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715194455/http://articles.latimes.com/2003/apr/13/magazine/tm-malkovich15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。弗朗切斯科·鲁利也特别参与了[[约翰·马克维奇|约翰·马克维奇]]的[[纪录片|纪录片]]“''Flipping Uncle Kimono''”的演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000518/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1|title=John Malkovich|work=IMDb|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306002132/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000518/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2134752/?ref_=tt_cl_t3|title=Francesco Rulli|work=IMDb|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317112013/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2134752/?ref_=tt_cl_t3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 事业 ==

2001年，弗朗切斯科·鲁利在纽约一场朋友的聚会中认识了[[约翰·马克维奇|约翰·马克维奇]]和大使{{tsl|en|Muhamed Sacirbey|穆罕默德·萨西尔贝}}，当时他问了马克维奇是否有兴趣做男装<ref>{{cite web|first=Joe|last=Brescia|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/11/business/11interview.html|title=From Broadway to Runway|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|date=February 11, 2006|accessdate=January 24, 2012|archive-date=2013-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719185255/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/11/business/11interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2002年，他们一起成立了“马德夫人”（Mrs. Mudd）<ref>{{cite web|title=Meet Mrs. Mudd|url=http://observer.com/2006/02/the-transom-50/|publisher=New York Observer|accessdate=13 February 2006|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206225619/http://observer.com/2006/02/the-transom-50/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一家专门出售马克维奇设计的服装的时装公司<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2004/07/09/1089000347671.html|title=Wearing John Malkovich|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=July 10, 2004|accessdate=January 24, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322084015/http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2004/07/09/1089000347671.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年，该公司发表了[[约翰·马克维奇|约翰·马克维奇]]男装系列"Uncle Kimono"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.royalcourttheatre.com/whats-on/john-malkovich-trunk-show|title=Let John Malkovich dress you…|date=April 30, 2005|accessdate=January 25, 2012|archive-date=2013-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126143351/http://www.royalcourttheatre.com/whats-on/john-malkovich-trunk-show|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该系列的设计风格显示出了马克维奇的奇特品味，例如系列中的"Nervous Breakdown Jacket"。

=== MTI USA 公司 ===

在过去的20多年里，MTI USA公司已发展和加强其交谈艺术的专长，在[[品牌|品牌]]和客户之间的对话<ref>{{cite web|title=Conversationalism for Brands|url=https://medium.com/@francescorulli/conversationalism-for-brands-f91a715cb1b5#.3j2am7acj|publisher=Medium|accessdate=2 February 2016|archive-date=2017-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110054427/https://medium.com/@francescorulli/conversationalism-for-brands-f91a715cb1b5#.3j2am7acj|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括涉及客户的兴趣和生活体验的观众细分。透过其专有平台Film Annex, [http://www.bitLanders.com bitLanders] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bitlanders.com/ |date=20200814204928 }}, [http://www.bitCharities.com bitCharities] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bitcharities.com/ |date=20180804164503 }}和[http://www.bit-Miles.com bitMiles] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bit-miles.com/ |date=20200315061601 }}，MTI USA公司已经掌握了如何与全球各地的用户建立关系和有意义的对话的知识。MTI USA公司的办事处设在[[欧洲|欧洲]]，[[美国|美国]]和[[台湾|台湾]]，这使得其专长可以合适地应用在当地的文化，传统和客户的期望。

=== Film Annex 平台 ===
在2006年，弗朗切斯科·鲁利创办了Film Annex网站，一个[[网络电视|网络电视]]网络，允许[[电影制片人|电影制片人]]创建免费的网络电视以展示他们的[[视频|影片]]作品。Film Annex努力地帮助电影制片人避免“正斜线心态”（forward-slash mentality），以他们的姓名，公司或影片计划去建立属于他们的品牌<ref>{{cite web|last=Park|first=Jane|title=Film Annex|url=https://creativecommons.org/weblog/entry/20865|work=Creative Commons Blog|publisher=Creative Commons|accessdate=26 January 2012|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907001706/http://creativecommons.org/weblog/entry/20865|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Film Annex平台的电影发行和网络电视，目的是以通过广告收入分享模式提供资助于艺术家和电影制片人的影片项目，并且推广他们的影片作品。其编辑团队在影片发布之前会审核其内容，以确保它们是由专业人士制作的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.constanceberjaut.com/rethinking-the-film-distribution/|title=» Rethinking the film distribution|publisher=|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206212622/http://www.constanceberjaut.com/rethinking-the-film-distribution/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 2010年5月，Film Annex与美国著名的编剧和导演[[阿貝爾·費拉拉|阿貝爾·費拉拉]]合作推出一个新的网络电视网站 [http://www.AbelFerrara.com www.AbelFerrara.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abelferrara.com/ |date=20120112040431 }}。该网络电视专门广播阿贝尔·费拉拉的视频，包括他的电影精选，关于他的最新影片项目的消息，他的采访视频，以及他的创作团队中的其他成员的采访视频。
* 2011年11月，Film Annex成为了美天发展集团（METAN Development Group）的在线发行商，主要在中国，美国和加拿大等地推广《Hello!好莱坞》系列<ref>{{cite web|title=Film Annex to Promote and Distribute Content Produced by METAN Development Group|url=http://www.onlineprnews.com/news/183178-1321045993-film-annex-to-promote-and-distribute-content-produced-by-metan-development-group.html|publisher=OnlinePRNews.com|accessdate=10 July 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031901/http://www.onlineprnews.com/news/183178-1321045993-film-annex-to-promote-and-distribute-content-produced-by-metan-development-group.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 2013年6月27日，Film Annex与[[馬修·莫汀|马修·摩丁]]的影片公司Cinco Dedos Peliculas合作<ref>{{cite web|title=Cinco Dedos Peliculas|url=http://www.imdb.com/company/co0322677/?ref_=fn_al_co_1|publisher=IMDB.com|accessdate=10 July 2013}}</ref>并重新发布他的一部短片，Jesus Was a Commie<ref>{{cite web|title=Matthew Modine Releases His Short Films on Film Annex's Online Film Distribution Platform|url=http://www.matthewmodine.com/news/show/id/11|publisher=MatthewModine.com|accessdate=10 July 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715022052/http://www.matthewmodine.com/news/show/id/11|archivedate=2013年7月15日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Matthew Modine Web TV Only on Film Annex|url=http://nakedfilmmaking.com/2013/07/01/watch-matthew-modines-film-jesus-was-a-commie-free-online-now/|publisher=NakedFilmMaking.com|accessdate=10 July 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212538/http://nakedfilmmaking.com/2013/07/01/watch-matthew-modines-film-jesus-was-a-commie-free-online-now/|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，和其他的影片项目。

=== BitLanders 和 BitCharities 平台===

2014年，弗朗切斯科·鲁利推出了bitLanders，一个[[社交网络|社交网络]]平台，拥有超过600,000名的注册用户与其扩展出的180万个社交连系的网络。[http://bitLanders.com bitLanders.com] {{Wayback|url=http://bitlanders.com/ |date=20150607142906 }}以一系列的任务游戏化了[[比特币|比特币]]和[[慈善|慈善]][[捐款|捐款]]，让用户可以透过bitCharities.com捐赠[[比特币|比特币]]给30多个非利润的和领先的[[慈善机构|慈善机构]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Exclusive: An Insight into Francesco Rulli’s Work and Thoughts|url=http://www.newsbtc.com/2015/05/17/exclusive-an-insight-into-francesco-rullis-work-and-thoughts|publisher=Newsbtc|accessdate=17 May 2015|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307064120/http://www.newsbtc.com/2015/05/17/exclusive-an-insight-into-francesco-rullis-work-and-thoughts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 阿富汗城堡软件公司（Afghan Citadel Software Company） ===

2012年，Film Annex推出了的另一个项目，弗朗切斯科·鲁利和阿富汗城堡软件公司（ACSC；Afghan Citadel Software Company）的[[创始人|创始人]]兼[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]{{tsl|en|Roya Mahboob|Roya Mahboob}}，一起发起了阿富汗发展项目（Afghan Development Project）和妇女附件（Women's Annex）。该项目旨在透过播放[[时事|时事]]视频，访谈视频和[[新闻|新闻]]剪辑让全世界看到[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]的正面发展，其中也包含了由阿富汗青年发展（ Afghan Youth Development）计划所提供的档案资料<ref>{{cite web|last=Shah|first=Angela|title=In Afghanistan, Roya Mahboob Connects Girls With Computers|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/01/in-afghanistan-roya-mahboob-connects-girls-with-computers.html|publisher=Newsweek's The Daily Beast|accessdate=5 September 2012|archive-date=2017-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217132839/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/01/in-afghanistan-roya-mahboob-connects-girls-with-computers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Roya Mahboob藉由弗朗切斯科·鲁利的帮助，在阿富汗境内40所学校里提供了学生们技术上的培训，并且表示这是阿富汗女孩开阔眼界的一个机会<ref>{{cite web|title=Afghan Women Help Drive Resurgent Economy|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/afghan-women-help-drive-recurrent-economy/1628696.html|publisher=Voice of America|accessdate=3 April 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211539/http://www.voanews.com/content/afghan-women-help-drive-recurrent-economy/1628696.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。妇女附件（Women's Annex）是一个教育性和融资的倡议，为妇女提供辅导和货币化他们发布在社交媒体上的任何视频内容，使他们能够有机会开始电影制作事业。

== 柔道 ==

弗朗切斯科·鲁利是{{tsl|en|New York Athletic Club|纽约体育俱乐部}}的一名成员<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nyac.org/default.aspx?p=DynamicModule&pageid=236060&ssid=89470&vnf=1 |title=New York Athletic Club's Judo Club |access-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005152621/http://www.nyac.org/default.aspx?p=DynamicModule&pageid=236060&ssid=89470&vnf=1 |archive-date=2011-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，该俱乐部的主席是Kevin Earls和Owen Tunney，弗朗切斯科·鲁利是4级黑带（Yodan），同时他在[[柔道|柔道]]竞争中也很活跃。他是一名教练，并帮助NYAC星期六的早晨节目的运行，该节目是为NYAC成员的子女接受柔道基本训练所举办的<ref>{{cite journal|last=DiPrinzio|first=Ron|title=Coaches Return for 111th Season|journal=The Winged Foot|date=October 2006|volume=125|issue=10|pages=10|url=http://members.nyac.org/files/October%2006%20Issue.pdf|accessdate=26 January 2012|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913231707/https://members.nyac.org/files/October%2006%20Issue.pdf|archive-date=2017-09-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

弗朗切斯科·鲁利是[http://judoarts.com/ JudoArts.com] {{Wayback|url=http://judoarts.com/ |date=20160307222236 }}的制片人。Film Annex和鲁利赞助了2013年的纽约柔道公开赛（New York Judo Open）。大赛的董事们是Mel Appelbaum，{{tsl|en|Arthur Canario|Arthur Canario}}博士和John Walla。 Film Annex拍摄了锦标赛和2010年以来与运动员们的采访<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teamusa.org/USA-Judo/Features/2010/October/15/Film-Annex-to-Sponsor-Promote-and-Document-the-New-York-Open-Judo-Championship-this-Weekend.aspx|title=Film Annex to Sponsor- Promote- and Document the New York Open Judo Championship this Weekend|work=Team USA|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924133053/http://www.teamusa.org/USA-Judo/Features/2010/October/15/Film-Annex-to-Sponsor-Promote-and-Document-the-New-York-Open-Judo-Championship-this-Weekend.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorkopenjudo.com/index.php|title=NewYorkOpenJudo - Home|publisher=|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210957/http://www.newyorkopenjudo.com/index.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作为柔道的支持者，鲁利和马克维奇呈现出了一个标新立异的时装秀，并且纪录在纪录片“Flipping Uncle Kimono”里，他们以20名柔道运动员作为模特儿，他们穿着马克维奇的时装公司“马德夫人”（Mrs. Mudd）设计的时尚系列的服装，该时装秀看起来像是冠军柔道比赛的竞争者穿着男士西装。该秀展的展台是在米兰的一个院子里，鲁利和马克维奇在现场观众面前共同指导演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0445020/plotsummary?ref_=tt_ov_pl|title=John Malkovich: Flipping Uncle Kimono (TV Movie 2005)|work=IMDb}}</ref>。

== 慈善 ==

弗朗切斯科·鲁利的公司Film Annex出资赞助了入榜2013[[时代百大人物|时代百大人物]]的Roya Mahboob在阿富汗的[[赫拉特|赫拉特]]和[[喀布尔|喀布尔]]开设11间教室和2间独立的IT中心，这使得55,000名女学生能够连接[[万维网|万维网]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Afghan women on the march by US Secretary of State John Kerry|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/11/john-kerry-afghan-women-roya-mahboob-99969.html|publisher=Politico|accessdate=18 November 2013|archive-date=2015-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508164415/http://www.politico.com/story/2013/11/john-kerry-afghan-women-roya-mahboob-99969.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。鲁利是全球医疗救助基金会（Global Medical Relief Fund）的顾问委员会委员，该基金会旨在援助受伤儿童或因战争，自然灾害而贻误病情的儿童<ref>{{cite web|title=Board Members|url=http://www.gmrfchildren.org/about-us/|work=GMRF Children|publisher=gmrfchildren.org|accessdate=10 July 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319093204/http://www.gmrfchildren.org/about-us/|archive-date=2016-03-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他是数字公民基金（Digital Citizen Fund）的创始成员（其前身为妇女附件Women's Annex ）<ref>{{cite web|title=If I teach them, no one can stop them": Roya Mahboob is fighting to educate the girls of Afghanistan|url=http://www.salon.com/2015/03/08/if_i_teach_them_no_one_can_stop_them_roya_mahboob_is_fighting_to_educate_the_girls_of_afghanistan|publisher=SALON|accessdate=8 March 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133716/http://www.salon.com/2015/03/08/if_i_teach_them_no_one_can_stop_them_roya_mahboob_is_fighting_to_educate_the_girls_of_afghanistan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鲁利以及{{tsl|en|Porter Bibb}}和Alan McFarland是南安普敦多媒体中心（Southampton Multimedia Center）的创始成员，它是一个为当地社区设置的数位素养教育和培训设施<ref>{{cite web|title=Hamptons Smart Phone Film Project Mentors Young Filmmakers|url=http://www.hamptons.com/The-Arts/Art-News/20712/Hamptons-Smart-Phone-Film-Project-Mentors-Young.html#.VWzu_WC1jGu|publisher=Hamptons.com|accessdate=28 April 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053926/http://www.hamptons.com/The-Arts/Art-News/20712/Hamptons-Smart-Phone-Film-Project-Mentors-Young.html#.VWzu_WC1jGu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

